  "text": "Specifically, I'm trying to grasp an understanding first of the process of experiencing third density before the veil so that I can a better understanding of the present process. As I understand it, the mind, body, spirit complexes went through the process of what we call physical incarnation in this density, but there was no forgetting. What was the benefit or purpose of the physical incarnation when there was no forgetting? I am Ra the purpose of incarnation in third density is to learn the ways of love.",
